{"tid":1285444,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"睇完果燃台對魚蛋革命既紀錄片有少少感想","createTime":"2019-07-04T14:42:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T17:59:36.000Z","uid":98472,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dce2226e2ae28d12117d25780135ba27c01e5f06","tid":1285444,"uid":98472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:42:20.000Z","msg":"今日訂閱左蘋果先發現果燃台D片咁豐富<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝蘋果還原成件事既前因後果, 特別片尾播每個義士既資料真係好震撼<br />\n每一個都係有血有肉既年青人, 因為依件事奉上左前途<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班義士真係好撚勇武, 真係由衷佩服<br />\n<br />\n本民前各成員及魚革每位參與者, 請受小弟一拜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地唔可以比義士既血白流, 監白坐<br />\n我地一定要繼承佢地既意志 (講緊幫襯多D小販)<br />\n黎緊星期六就係一個好好既機會, 繼佢地光復上水光復屯門之後, 我地要代埋佢地果份去光復屯門公園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.feature.appledaily.com/goodestchannel/video/5cd3f054c288fb00052bc510/%E9%AD%9A%E8%9B%8B%E8%AE%8A%E5%AD%90%E5%BD%88%E7%9A%8410%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%20%E9%87%8D%E7%B5%84%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E9%BB%91%E5%A4%9C%E9%82%A3%E5%B9%B4%E5%88%9D%E4%BA%8C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Fgoodestchannel%2Fvideo%2F5cd3f054c288fb00052bc510%2F%25E9%25AD%259A%25E8%259B%258B%25E8%25AE%258A%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%25BD%2588%25E7%259A%258410%25E5%25B0%258F%25E6%2599%2582%2520%25E9%2587%258D%25E7%25B5%2584%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592%25E9%25BB%2591%25E5%25A4%259C%25E9%2582%25A3%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2588%259D%25E4%25BA%258C&d=mquyjxz0VyBhytkWBmIwRQfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=d6c8fce4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Fgoodestchannel%2Fvideo%2F5cd3f054c288fb00052bc510%2F%25E9%25AD%259A%25E8%259B%258B%25E8%25AE%258A%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%25BD%2588%25E7%259A%